<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kaposter</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: myFirstFont;
            src: url('/sansation/Sansation_Regular.ttf');
        }
        h1 {
            font-family: myFirstFont;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #140000, #520505);
            color: rgb(253, 207, 113);
            font-family: "Raleway", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 34px;
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scrolling */
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 100%; /* Ensure container width does not exceed viewport */
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal overflow */
        }
        .text-shadow-sm {
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .space-x-4 {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .text-shadow-md {
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .h1, .h2, .h3, p {
            color: rgb(253, 207, 113);
        }
        .p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            word-spacing: 0.3em;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }
        .nav-link {
            transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            color: rgb(253, 207, 113);
        }
        .section {
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        .section.visible {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        .nav-bar {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: rgb(253, 207, 113);
            color: #000;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-shadow: none;
            transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: rgb(253, 207, 113);
        }
        .box {
            background-color: rgba(253, 207, 113, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid rgb(253, 207, 113);
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
                entries.forEach(entry => {
                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                        entry.target.classList.add('visible', 'animate__animated', 'animate__fadeInUp');
                    }
                });
            });

            document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach(section => {
                observer.observe(section);
            });
        });
    </script>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header id="home" class="section py-20 animate__delay-1s">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <br>
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-shadow-md" style="color: rgb(253, 207, 113);">Kaposter</h1>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
        <!-- About Section -->
        <section class="section py-10 animate__delay-2s">
            <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center text-shadow-sm p">
                Kaposter is a caring online platform that helps you and your loved ones share memories, offer condolences, and find support when someone passes away. Kaposter is here for you during difficult times.
            </p>
            
            <div class="mt-8 space-x-4">
                <a href="/signup.html" class="btn-primary">Start Creating Eulogies</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Key Features Section -->
        <section id="features" class="section py-10 animate__delay-2s">
            <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-center mb-5 text-shadow-md">Key Features</h2>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center space-y-4">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="p-5 box rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-plus fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-shadow-sm">Account Creation</h3>
                            <p>User can create account to access the platform to create a unique memorial link</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInRight animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="p-5 box rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                            <i class="fas fa-link fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-shadow-sm">Sharing Links</h3>
                            <p>Account holders can share unique links with a group of individuals, allowing them to contribute to a dedicated feed</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="p-5 box rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-up-from-bracket fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-shadow-sm">Memory Uploads</h3>
                            <p>Account holders can share unique links with a group of individuals, allowing them to contribute to a dedicated feed</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInRight animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="p-5 box rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                            <i class="fas fa-book fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-shadow-sm">Feed Page</h3>
                            <p>All uploaded memories are displayed in a chronological feed with captions and images, similar to social media platforms.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Benefits Section -->
        <section id="benefits" class="section py-10 animate__delay-1s">
            <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-5 text-shadow-md">Benefits</h2>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center space-y-4">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="p-5 box rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-shadow-sm">Emotional Support</h3>
                            <p>Kaposter provides a space for individuals to express their emotions, share memories, and offer condolences, fostering a sense of connection and support.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInRight animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="p-5 box rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                            <i class="fas fa-clock fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-shadow-sm">Convenience</h3>
                            <p>The platform's accessibility on mobile and desktop devices ensures that users can participate and contribute from anywhere at any time.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4 animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="p-5 box rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                            <i class="fas fa-lock fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-shadow-sm">Privacy and Security</h3>
                            <p>Kaposter prioritizes user privacy and data security, implementing measures to safeguard sensitive information shared on the platform.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
